About this item

  • 【Material】The remote control door lock with anti-rust battery box, the spring is made of special material, durable in use. The locking tab and main parts are stainless steel, no fading. Beautiful appearance and arc design, the lock body is relatively thin.
  • 【Electronic Deadbolt Door Lock】Our deadbolt access control system unlocks by remote control, then closes the door, locks 3 seconds later. (no lock, no lock). The remote control distance is 0-10m. The unlock mode includes remote control unlock and key unlock.
  • 【Wide Application】Remote controls with digital conversation system, cannot be decoded or duplicated. Ideal for office, home, hotel, anti-theft door, hall door, wooden doors, garage door, etc.
  • 【Easy to Install】Easy and firm installation with the external mounting plate. Remote control with digital conversation system, can not be decoded or duplicated. Innovative release and lock tone. It is easy to install without plugging in.
  • 【Power Saving Control Mode】Low power consumption, 4 AA batteries can offer about 1 year of work (not include 4 AA batteries). This smart lock has a long service life, 300 thousand lock operations, no wear.

Product Description

Electronic Deadbolt Set

Package Included:

1 x Door Lock(not include battery)

1 x Lock body bottom pinch plate

1 x Latch seat (Inside door, outside door can be used)

4 x Remote control

1 x 23A 12V battery for Remote control

1 x Instructions, 1 x Screw pack

Easy Installation on the Left or Right

Easy and firm installation with the external mounting plate. Remote control with digital conversation system, can not be decoded or duplicated. Innovative release and lock tone. It is easy to install without plugging in.

Remote Control Electronic Door Lock

Remote controls with digital conversation system, cannot be decoded or duplicated. Dual core dual system, faster, more responsive.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
